25|$|Laura M. Ricketts (born December 15, 1967) is {{co-owner}} of the Chicago Cubs. Ricketts is also {{a board member of}} Lambda Legal and the Housing <b>Opportunities</b> <b>for</b> <b>Women</b> organization. Ricketts' ownership stake in the Cubs is uniquely noteworthy because it makes her the first openly gay owner of a major-league sports franchise.|$|E
