50|$|The Pavlov First Saint-Petersburg State Medical University {{was founded}} in September 14 (26) 1897 as the Medical Institute <b>for</b> <b>Women.</b> It was the first {{institution}} in Europe that provided an <b>opportunity</b> <b>for</b> <b>women</b> to acquire higher medical education.|$|R
